  <logID>k__BackingField: ENTRY #0012
  logName: ARCHIVE_12_LIFE SUPPORT ANALYSIS
  locationFound: 
  logDescription: "Cleanser \r\nLOG ENTRY\r\nDate and time: 11/06 08:11:59\r\nIt\u2019s
    ironic how dependent humanity can be on nature while simultaneously destroying
    it. The tree in the conservatory, planted and raised by humans to produce oxygen
    to further fuel this ship. Using a product of the earth to further destroy it
    is deplorable. I will find a way to fly this ship without the use of this tree
    so it too can finally rest. I will of course keep it for my feathered friends
    that they may nest and be at peace."
  logImage: {fileID: 0}
